short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extensions allows to download the list of participants in a meeting in Microsoft Teams or Google Meet as a text file

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension is to test the users' preference on attendance tracking. In the next version, we will launch new features, containing timing tracking and participates' interaction during the meeting.
